project statement

Magic bubble: An interactive particle system that forms a blod/bubble. User can create,
move, change the scale of the bubble and pop it using a wand, hand gestures and saying
certain phrases(spells) outloud. The goal is to intearct with a digital object using
fluid and natural input. 

specific goals for the project

- create a particle system 
- develop intearctivity for only certain particles 
- first establish interactivity for mouse and touch events :create, move, scale and pop bubble
- second establish interactivity for leap motion or kinect 
- integrate sound into the output 
- bonus: make it a 3D hologram

